# SpacetimeDB Brand Styling

When building UI for SpacetimeDB applications, use the **official ClockworkLabs brand colors** from spacetimedb.com.

## Primary Brand Color

The official SpacetimeDB brand uses **green (#4cf490)** as the primary accent — not purple/cyan.

